ting memorable experiencies by embracing your unique vision of a perfect wedding.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Our Company\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #560570;\">Our Company\r\n</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nPlanning a destination wedding can be challenging, but itâ€™s a life time experience. In MY PERFECT WEDDING we believe that giving personalized approach and learning more about your envision of a perfect wedding and personalities, will ensure a memorable wedding.\r\n\r\nOur main goal is to provide high quality and personalized â€œhands-onâ€ service in order to exceed expectations. We assist couples in the entire planning process and recommend the best suppliers and venues in the area.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Our Founder\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #560570;\">Our Founder\r\n</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-401 alignleft\" src=\"http://77.104.156.53/~myperf20/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/michelle-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"michelle\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nStudied psicology in Mexico city, and worked in one of the most important hotels in the city Camino Real Polanco and later in the headquarters of Hoteles Camino Real. I love my profession and gives me the sensibility to know and learn from different people and cultures.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI started on the wedding business 7 years ago when I came to live to this paradise, my â€œhomeâ€, Playa del Carmen. Had the opportunity to work in one of the most luxurious hotels in the area Banyan Tree Mayakoba since the opening in the Romance department, which influenced me to be detailed and costume service oriented.\r\nWhen a new opportunity to begin my own business came knocking my door y didnâ€™t hesitate and started this new adventure. And never realized that this breakthrough will come with another adventure of being a mom at the same time. So my world happily changed completely.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI am truly passionate about weddings and love to be there for our couples, at the end of each wedding I feel so thankful that all the hard work is reflected as a beautiful event and the most important satisfaction is to have most of our brides as friends after the wedding\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" module_id=\"review_title\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #560570;\">Reviews</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_code admin_label=\"Code\"]&lt;section id=\'grid_reviews\'&gt; &lt;span class=\'grid-line right\'&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=\'grid-line right second\'&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=\'grid-line bottom\'&gt;&lt;/span&gt; [grid_reviews] &lt;/section&gt;[/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2016-10-03 22:46:28','2016-10-03 22:46:28','',39,'http://77.104.156.53/~myperf20/index.php/39-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(407,1,'2016-10-03 22:53:20','2016-10-03 22:53:20','Working with Michelle made an enormous difference in planning my wedding in Play del Carmen. She was extremely knowledgeable about local vendors and helped to have her be in Mexico when planning from the United States. Her recommendations were always spot on and exceeded expectations. The weekend of the event she kept things organized and everything on schedule. We even had some crazy circumstances and she was a calming force keeping everything going and together. I would recommend Michelle to anyone and hire her again!','Lauren Epstein','','inherit','closed','closed','','131-autosave-v1','','','2016-10-03 22:53:20','2016-10-03 22:53:20','',131,'http://77.104.156.53/~myperf20/index.php/131-autosave-v1',0,'revision','',0),(408,1,'2016-10-03 22:54:17','2016-10-03 22:54:17','My Perfect Wedding made beautiful gift bags for our destination wedding. They worked with our price requirements for our 80 guests and made sure that every touch was perfect. From the bottles of champagne to the personalized bags to the treats inside, everything was done in great taste! Thank you so much!','Coleen Deal','','publish','closed','closed','','coleen-deal-2','','','2016-10-03 22:54:17','2016-10-03 22:54:17','',0,'http://77.104.156.53/~myperf20/?post_type=review&#038;p=408',0,'review','',0),(409,1,'2016-10-03 22:56:45','2016-10-03 22:56:45','I just got back from my honeymoon and had to write a review about my amazing wedding planner Michelle. Since the beginning of my wedding planning I found Michelle through looking at blogs of other weddings in Mexico, she came highly recommended a bride who I e-mailed. Michelle was seriously the best planner I could of asked for. She took care of every single detail so that I didn\'t have to worry about a thing during my wedding weekend. I had three full days of events-welcome fiesta, wedding, and sunday brunch and she executed each event so perfectly! If you are getting married in Mexico I would HIGHLY recommend usi